      • setPolyPathMode

        public void setPolyPathMode(PolyPath.PathMode m)
        Indicate polygons will be output and set the path mode to be output. This must be called before the first write command, otherwise any attempts to write a polygon will result in a warning and no polygon written. The default mode is PolyPath.PathMode.MORPHING.
        Parameters:
        m - mode to write polygons.

      • clearPolyPathMode

        Indicate that no polygons will be output (the default).
